Class Summary
Attribute An attribute.
BadRegexError Alert which indicates that a malformed regex pattern was specified for a gxp:param
ConflictingAttributesError Alert which indicates that an element has two different attributes when only one of either is allowed.
DuplicateImportError Alert which indicates that a duplicate Import was found.
IllegalVariableNameError Alert which indicates that an illegal variable name was encountered.
InvalidDoctypeError Alert which indicates that an invalid doctype was specified in gxp:doctype
InvalidRootError Alert which indicates that the root element of the document was something invalid.
InvalidTypeError Alert which indicates that an invalid type was specified.
MismatchedTemplateNameError An Alert that indicates that the specified template name doesn't match the file name.
MisplacedJavaAnnotationError An ErrorAlert which indicates that a JavaAnnotation with an what inapropriate for the current context was encountered.
MissingAttributesError Alert which indicates that an element requires at least one of the specified attributes, but none were provided.
MoreThanOneConstructorError Alert which indicates that more than one <gxp:constructor>s were found for a single template.
NoClausesInCondError An ErrorAlert which indicates that a gxp:cond with no clauses was encountered.
ReparentedTree The output of Reparenter.
Reparenter Moves gxp:attr, gxp:param, gxp:import and gxp:throws into their parent elements.
RequiresStaticContentError Alert which indicates that a node that requires static content was found, but it contained dynamic content.
UnknownContentTypeError Alert which indicates that a unknown content type was encountered.
